revised the material studied by Casanueva and considered those as belonging to an unidentified Lycosinae species. Based in an exemplar from the 
<typeStatus id="B13B88129C02FFF9FF10F8A9FF53F8E6" box="[151,199,1847,1871]" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">type</typeStatus>
locality, identified by Mello-Leitão as 
<taxonomicName id="A9804D339C02FFF9FDFCF8A9FC16F8E6" authority="Capocasale" authorityName="Capocasale" box="[635,898,1846,1871]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Araucaniocosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="difficilis">
<emphasis id="5CF4EAA29C02FFF9FDFCF8A9FD62F8E6" box="[635,758,1846,1871]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">A. difficilis</emphasis>
, Capocasale
</taxonomicName>
proposed this species as a junior synonym of 
<emphasis id="5CF4EAA29C02FFF9FA03F8A9FEB4F8DA" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">
<taxonomicName id="A9804D339C02FFF9FA03F8A9FE88F8DA" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Allocosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">A. brasiliensis</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Although we did not examine the 
<typeStatus id="B13B88129C02FFF9FD21F8C4FC9FF8DA" box="[678,779,1882,1907]" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">holotype</typeStatus>
, the morphology of the male bulb and the body size in the original description provided by Mello-Leitão seems to be different from 
<taxonomicName id="A9804D339C02FFF9FC6FF8E1FB1EF83E" box="[1000,1162,1918,1943]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Allocosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">
<emphasis id="5CF4EAA29C02FFF9FC6FF8E1FB1EF83E" box="[1000,1162,1918,1943]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">A. brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Therefore we consider that the examination of the 
<typeStatus id="B13B88129C02FFF9FE4CF83CFDB9F812" box="[459,557,1954,1979]" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="A9804D339C02FFF9FDD5F83DFD59F812" box="[594,717,1954,1979]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Araucaniocosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="difficilis">
<emphasis id="5CF4EAA29C02FFF9FDD5F83DFD59F812" box="[594,717,1954,1979]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="264">A. difficilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
will provide arguments to elucidate the taxonomic status of this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
